WEBVTT

00:00:03.539 --> 00:00:06.615
Znate, probudite se ujutro,

00:00:06.615 --> 00:00:09.135
odjenete se, obujete,

00:00:09.135 --> 00:00:11.647
krenete u svijet.

00:00:11.647 --> 00:00:15.898
Planirate se vratiti, razodjenuti,

00:00:15.898 --> 00:00:18.123
otići u krevet,

00:00:18.123 --> 00:00:19.877
probuditi se, napraviti sve ponovno.

00:00:19.877 --> 00:00:23.025
I to nam iščekivanje, taj ritam,

00:00:23.025 --> 00:00:25.295
daje strukturu načinu

00:00:25.295 --> 00:00:28.883
na koji organiziramo sami sebe i svoje živote

00:00:28.883 --> 00:00:32.363
te mu daje mjeru predvidljivosti.